  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Oscar at his biggest. Low fundamental offset brings the voice down to bass territory. Full partials with negative tilt emphasize the deep harmonics. Despite the size, everything is gentle — low effort, moderate drama, slow vibrato. Like standing next to the largest creature in the room and realizing it only wants to be friends.",
